      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781113699371,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Since constructor is public, \nmultiple instances of it can be created easily \nby calling the Constructor",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Since constructor is public, \nmultiple instances of it can be created easily \nby calling the Constructor",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Vh1BvvdsJBYXGQrlNmvhp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 322.40234375,
      "y": 697.77734375,
      "width": 682.03955078125,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aA",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 518096487,
      "version": 303,
      "versionNonce": 444463446,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781113690640,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "To avoid multiple instances, we need to make the constructor Private\nand hide from directly accessing\n- keep static Class member & make constructor private\n- static members belong to class and not to objects\n- create new instance only if member is null",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "To avoid multiple instances, we need to make the constructor Private\nand hide from directly accessing\n- keep static Class member & make constructor private\n- static members belong to class and not to objects\n- create new instance only if member is null",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "20YIu2UPC1iOd4A5abqvp",
